woman headmistress~
Mary Kramer~
Leaning back on her chair is the Headmistress of the Garden.
~
Being apponited the position from her family line, Mary runs Balamb
Garden with a nerve quite unlike another. Participating in the
daily activities, she makes sure that the next generation of SeeDs
is available to fight the SorceresS.
Looking at you, she smiles as she asks what you want.
~
