luc girl sorceror~
Luc Nihial~
A beautiful girl in silk, nomadic clothing is meditating in the air.
~
A mystic knight of the eastern magi clan, this Sorceror is here on
request of her leader to speak with Mary Kramer, Headmistress of
Balamb Gardens.
Hoping to unite forces against the battle with the SorceresS, Luc
will do whatever it takes for the salvation of her fellow clan
members.
Just by looking at her, you can feel the sheer power that lies
within this beautiful girl and you have the feeling that you dont
want to find out its limit.
~
