#33000
Center of Balamb Garden~
All around you lies Balamb Garden, the starting institute of students wishing
to become SeeDs. Spreading out in all directions, this school teaches a newbie
everything they need to know against the dangers of the outside world. Right
in front of your eyes however is a huge terminal screen used by the students
to get infomation on the whereabouts of the Garden. Maybe you should use it?
~
